3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with generating realistic face images using user-supplied attributes, which involves AI techniques. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating high-quality face images, which is a multimedia application. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with generating realistic face images, which involves graphics techniques.
